    <p>I am Yongtak Kim, an AWS Cloud Support Engineer and OpenSearch SME.</p>
    <p>My work centers on customer troubleshooting, analytics workload support, and turning repeated support engineering decisions into reliable AI-assisted workflows. I started from mobile app and backend product development, then expanded into image processing, data platforms, cloud analytics, and AI-agent tooling.</p>

    <h2>What I Work On</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>OpenSearch customer issue analysis and troubleshooting</li>
      <li>Analytics support across AWS services</li>
      <li>Support-agent persona design and verification rules</li>
      <li>MCP-based workflows that connect Slack, Outlook, wiki knowledge, ticket search, and local tools</li>
      <li>Developer productivity tools for AI-agent session search, handoff, and documentation</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Selected Tools</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/ytkim4558/claude-resume">claude-resume</a>: LLM-summary-based TUI for finding and resuming Claude Code sessions</li>
